The paper discusses the use of smartphones for affect sensing, which involves human-computer interaction (HCI) and multimedia (MM) technologies. Therefore, cs.HC and cs.MM are the most likely categories. The paper also discusses the use of facial expression and voice, which are related to computer vision (cs.CV) and speech processing (cs.SD). Finally, the paper discusses the challenges of privacy, which is related to cybersecurity (cs.CY).
